Created attachment 192743
[PATCH] [DOC UPDATE] Mirroring FreeBSD, Section 2.4. (Services to Offer), r51585

freebsd.org/doc/en_US.ISO8859-1/articles/hubs/mirror-requirements.html;

  * replaced www/apache22 by www/apache24;
  * changed www/boa's description (avoiding flamewars?);
  * added www/cherokee and www/lighttpd web servers to the list;
  * Nginx -> nginx (as used by the project);
  * minor fixes, again, to avoid any flamewar.

All added/changed descriptions are based on respective ports' pkg-descr.
